snippet.textDisplay: doctor, thank you! I found your videos while looking for someone explaining the EKG. you did it in such a beautiful way and now I can clap the rhythms of the heart. you are brilliant and amazing and you have a great language. thank you! from a medical student in Copenhagen that misses classes so much.
